title: Part C
stimulusHtml:
1 point is earned for: g(10)

1 point is earned for: g(108)

1 point is earned for: g'(108)

1 point is earned for the equation of tangent line

g(0) = 0 and the function values of g increase by 2 for every increase of 5 in x.

g(10) = 2g(5) = 4

g( 108 )= ∫ 0 105 f( t ) dt+ ∫ 105 108 f( t ) dt             =21g( 5 )+g( 3 )=44 MathType@MTEF@5@5@@66D7@

g'(108) = f(108) = f(3) = 2

An equation for the line tangent to the graph of g at x = 108 is y - 44 = 2(x - 108).
